INTRODUCTION
============
his file describes the basic steps to install Simple DBMail Admin on your
web server. For additional information, write an Email at claas.kaehler@akator.de



REQUIREMENTS
============
 * DBMail
 * MySQL or PostgreSQL
 * Apache or nginx... or whatever.
 * PHP <= 5.3 


INSTALLATION
============

1. Decompress and put this folder somewhere inside your document root
2. Edit the config.php and enter your database config and enter the loging data for the webinterface
7. Done!
